{"tid":2075226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍擬提議日本擁有攻擊敵方基地能力 被轟蹂躪憲法","createTime":"2020-06-22T16:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T17:19:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fe0fc1f5ce773ded9d2e59e0c236162b5cb49e","tid":2075226,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"（中央社記者楊明珠東京22日專電）日本決定停止部署「陸基神盾」飛彈防禦計畫，首相安倍晉三18日表示，將調整安全保障戰略，考慮是否擁有攻擊敵方基地能力。日本共產黨書記局長小池晃今天痛批安倍蹂躪憲法。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n小池指出，安倍政府原本計畫引進美國製新型彈道飛彈攔截系統「陸基神盾」（Aegis Ashore），現在出現破綻，決定撤銷部署計畫，安倍為了掩飾自己的醜態，於是趁危亂之際要開始研議是否擁有「攻擊敵方基地能力」，這絕對無法被容許。<br />\n<br />\n有關「攻擊敵方基地能力」，小池指出，這是先發制人的攻擊，如果招致反擊，將蒙受巨大損害。擁有攻擊性的武器完全是在蹂躪憲法，絕對不能被容許。這與專守防衛的想法是完全矛盾的。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n自民黨內部有人認為要研議是否擁有「攻擊敵方基地能力」，事情來得太突然。公明黨內部則是持反對意見。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n（編輯：林治平）1090623<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006230004.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202006230004.aspx&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7oD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=ee42a113\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006230004.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"697305f874a4f8b449db592ce5b30d18c1c449eb","tid":2075226,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"南海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209cc28497e9bcb57e2d56b1d2635c8f8961122a","tid":2075226,"uid":131121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"日本共產黨仲有勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"a751178276c8f9faa759a061fd25e665d70d4147","tid":2075226,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"209cc28497e9bcb57e2d56b1d2635c8f